title: Problems after Analysing a Video

labels.name: howtousedlc
labels.description: issue regarding the use of DeepLabCut

body:
Hei,
[Windows 10, DeepLabCut Version '2.1.10.4', in Anaconda Env and GUI]

I have the following problem. 
I would like to analyse a mouse in the open field video using DLC-GUI and have started a multianimal project for this, because I have also labelled the open field (correct?).
Then I have successfully trained DLC with 10 videos of 20 frames each. All labels are displayed correctly in the GUI.
(200000 iterations, ellipse)

The analysis of the videos also seems to work, but in the output folder I only get the "meta.pickle" and "full.pickle" but no csv or .h5 output. What could be the reason for this? The csv/h5 files are only displayed after the refinement. 

Reproduction:
1) click on "Analyze Video" 
2) load config.yaml
3) load video file (.mpg)
output =  meta/full.pickle
4) Convert to tracklets
output = _el.pickle (used for refinement)
5) checking for csv in folder failed
